title: Stoneleigh at the Reserve – Your comfortable, quiet getaway! 1 bed, 1 bath
posting_body: ['1 Bedroom  1 Bathroom | 720 - 730 sq ft | $1445 - $1520/Month', 'Stoneleigh at the Reserve', '5200 Annapolis Ln N', 'Plymouth, MN 55446', 'show contact info', 'Description:', "The only thing that rivals Stoneleigh's exceptional property is our premium location that's just 15 miles northwest of Minneapolis.", "Here you'll have easy access to I-494, and a public bus stop is just steps outside our front door.", "The Reserve Park is a five-minute walk down the street: it's a great place to have a picnic, go for a walk, or let the kids run and play.", "Just down the road, you'll find Rockford Road Plaza where you can pick up necessities at Target, grab a quick burger at Five Guys, and discover the latest fashions at Kohl's.", 'Apartment Amenities:', '● Built-In Office/Desk', 'In Select Units', '● Ceiling Fans In Select Units', '● Dishwasher', '● Full-Size Washer/Dryer in Every Home', '● Garbage Disposal', '● Linen Closet', '● Pantry In Select Units', '● Patio/Balcony In Select Units', '● Vaulted Ceiling In Select Units', '● Walk-In Closets In Select Units', 'Our Residents Enjoy:', '● Car Wash Bay', '● Coffee Station', '● Conference Room', '● Elevator', '● Fitness Center', '● Gameroom', '● Picnic Area', '● Pool', '● Recycling', '● Resident Lounge', '● Basketball Half-Court', '● Business Center', '● Cardio Machines', '● Complimentary DVD/Video Rental', '● Controlled Access Building', '● On-site Maintenance & Management', '● Planned Social Activities', '● Racquetball Court', '● Reserveable Clubhouse', '● Wake Up With Weidner Continental Breakfast', 'Additional Details:', 'Deposit: Call', 'Terms: Variable', 'Pets: Dogs and Cats Allowed:', 'Fees and deposits apply, please contact the community office for additional information.', '100 lb Weight Limit.', '2 Pet Limit.', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '14C03077AC4348F5']
